{"word":"G5524 - χορηγέω - chorēgéō - khor-ayg-eh'-o - Give","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χορηγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chorēgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khor-ayg-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அளி, தந்தருள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to be a chorus - leader, lead a chorus"},{"paragraph":"2. to furnish the chorus at one's own expense"},{"paragraph":"3. to supply, furnish abundantly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G5525 - χορός - chorós - khor-os'/5525\">G5525</a> and <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to be a <i>dance leader</i>, that is, (genitive case) to <i>furnish:</i> - give, minister.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5524/5524\">G5524</a>, <a href=\"#/G5525/5525\">G5525</a>"}]}